<F P=103> LD2105174494 </F>
<F P=104>  Tehran IRNA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Tehran, May 21, IRNA -- The students and staff of 
the Qom Theological Centre felicitated the leader of the Islamic 
revolution, Ayatollah Seyyed 'Ali Khamene'i here Saturday [21 
May] on the occasion of 'Id-ul-Adha and deplored the unislamic 
attitude of Saudi rulers. 
  "Although Muslims feel bitter about the Saudi regime's 
banning of the disavowal of polytheists rally, as was evident in 
