  [Text] Baghdad, 22 May (INA) -- Foreign Minister Muhammad 
Sa'id al-Sahhaf has condemned the announcement to secede from 
united Yemen made by 'Ali Salim al-Bid late Saturday night, 21 
May. 
  In a statement to INA, the foreign minister said Iraq 
