<H4>    Russia Reportedly Recognizes South </H4>

<F P=102> NC2105100094 Cairo MENA in Arabic 0940 GMT 21 May 94 </F>
<F P=103> NC2105100094 </F>
<F P=104>  Cairo MENA </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Excerpt] Sanaa, 21 May (MENA)--Yemeni Planning Minister 
Dr. 'Abd-al-Karim al-Iryani said in Sanaa today that the Russian 
Federation Republic has recognized the Yemeni Democratic 
Republic. [passage omitted] 

</TEXT>

