<H4>    Al-Iryani Denies Russian Action </H4>

<F P=102> NC2105152094 Cairo MENA in Arabic 1505 GMT 21 May 94 </F>
<F P=103> NC2105152094 </F>
<F P=104>  Cairo MENA </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Sanaa, 21 May (MENA)--Dr. 'Abd-al-Karim al-Iryani, 
Yemeni minister of planning and development, has denied that 
Russia has recognized the Yemeni Democratic Republic, saying 
that apparently there has been a misunderstanding. 

</TEXT>

