<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Reaction to Al-Bid Secession Call Noted </PHRASE></F></HT>
<H4>    Yemeni Renaissance Assails Move </H4>

<F P=102> JN2205195894 Sanaa Yemeni Republic Radio Network in Arabic 
1700 GMT 22 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> JN2205195894 </F>
<F P=104>  Sanaa Yemeni Republic Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The Yemeni Renaissance Movement has declared its 
categorical and vigorous rejection of the historical crime of 
secession committed by the secessionist gang in the Yemeni 
Socialist Party [YSP]. The movement called the move high 
treason against God, the homeland, and the people. 
  In a statement it issued today, the Renaissance Movement 
emphasized that it supports the legal leadership as it defends 
Yemen's unity, and urged the unionists inside the YSP -- the top 
and lower echelons alike -- to speak out against this step and 
join a national effort to thwart that evil plan. 

</TEXT>

