  [Text] A responsible military source at the command of the 
armed forces of the Democratic Republic of Yemen has said that 
the forces of the adventurous al-Ahmar gang not only failed to 
adhere to the cease-fire announced on evening of 20 May, but had 
in fact escalated the fighting on all fronts. It unleashed 
large forces in all directions. More serious than this, it used 
rockets in its criminal acts. 
  Last night, the inhabitants of the quiet and peaceful city 
of 
