Republic of Yemen and the blessed 'Id al-Adha, were surprised by 
a rocket which fell in a heavily populated area killing and 
wounding peaceful women and children. Meanwhile, the air 
defense forces of the Democratic Republic of Yemen succeeded in 
shooting down a similar rocket in the air. 
  The responsible source confirmed that this was a criminal 
act 
and was part of the series of the terrible crimes of the family 
of al-Ahmar, under the leadership of war general 'Ali 'Abdallah 
Salih. 
  The armed forces of the Democratic Republic of Yemen reserve 
for themselves the right to retaliate forcefully against these 
stupid and crazy acts of the bloody al-Ahmar gang. 

