<H3> <TI>   Salih Chairs Joint Leadership Meeting 20 May </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Salih Chairs Joint Leadership Meeting 20 May </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   JN2105044594 Sanaa Yemeni Republic Radio Network in Arabic 
0330 GMT 21 May 94 </F>

