  [Text] In the name of the people, recognizing Articles 12 
and 14, paragraph A of the declaration of the establishment of 
the Democratic Republic of Yemen; confirming the provisional 
National Salvation Council's statement endorsed in the meeting 
held on 21 May 1994 regarding the appointment of a speaker for 
