  [Excerpt] The command of God has been delivered, so don't 
be too persistent. This is what we tell the gang of apostasy 
and secession. This is because the announcement of secession 
made by the traitor 'Ali Salim al-Bid is evidence that his hour 
and that of his gang has come and that God's command will be 
implemented at the hands of his honest slaves of the sons of 
Yemen in the battles of honor and sacrifice and on the axes of 
