blindness to guidance and violated their commitment and pledge 
to God, so He led them astray, blinded them, and promised them 
severe punishment. 
  They have thought their weapons would save them from God and 
the people. But God surprised them and threw panic into their 
hearts and made the unionists stand firm. Thus, all the people 
are now fighting the battle against al-Bid and his gang. The 
gang is now closer to falling in the abyss and very near its end. 
  Have they not heard the marching of the forces of legitimacy 
and unity when these forces continued to capture locations, 
hardware, and various weapons? Have they not learned that the 
forces which they had controlled are daily joining the forces of 
legitimacy in all positions? Have they not heard that the 
nationalist parties and popular bodies and organizations have 
all condemned their grave traitorous act? Have they not heard 
the unionists within the Yemeni Socialist Party condemn this 
malicious secessionist crime and disown this malevolent 
traitorous action? Have they not seen the world ridicule their 
traitorous action? 
  Indeed, they have heard and seen all of this. We shall leave 
them in their trespasses, to wander in distraction. [Koranic 
verse] They are embarking on an adventure and are shooting 
their arrows right and left. Therefore, what they have done so 
far, and what they will do, are no more than random acts 
committed in the dark. [passage omitted] 

</TEXT>

