<F P=102>   LD2305203894 Algiers ENTV Television Network in Arabic 1900 
GMT 23 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2305203894 </F>
<F P=104>  Algiers ENTV Television Network </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Excerpt] An investigation has taken place into a breakout 
from Tazoult prison on 10 March, the circumstances in which the 
incident occurred, and the share of responsibility for the 
incident of public officials. Following the investigation, the 
governor of Batna Province, the head of security of Batna 
Province, the head of security of Tazoult district, the director 
of re-education affairs at the Ministry of Justice, and the 
Tazoult police chief were dismissed today. 
  The first results of the investigation revealed that the 
terrorists had benefited from the assistance of two persons 
working at the police station. [passage omitted] 

</TEXT>

