  [Text] The Cairo agreement on the implementation of self- 
government in Gaza and Jericho will be translated into Arabic in 
order to make even the junior Palestinian officers in Gaza and 
Jericho familiar with it. Our correspondent Moti Amir reports 
that it has emerged that the Palestinian leaders have failed to 
explicate the written details of the agreement to the 
Palestinian population and security forces. A Palestinian 
source told our correspondent that the Palestinian leaders often 
prefer to explain events on the ground in their own way and 
contrary to the agreement, perhaps in order to win the 
Palestinian public's support. 

