BFN 

  [Excerpts] [Announcer] A deadly stampede occurred yesterday 
in al-Mina [holy site near Mecca] during the stoning of Satan 
[pilgrims throw stones at three idols representing Satan] which 
caused the death of 182 pilgrims. Preliminary reports from our 
our mission in the holy places say that 13 Algerians may be 
among the victims. 
