<H4>    U.S. Reaction Noted </H4>

<F P=102> JN2405064894 Sanaa Yemeni Republic Radio Network in Arabic 
0430 GMT 24 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> JN2405064894 </F>
<F P=104>  Sanaa Yemeni Republic Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The U.S. State Department yesterday denounced 
al-Bid's secessionist announcement and called for political 
dialogue. 
  According to AFP, State Department Spokesman Michael McCurry 
said the United States will not reply to al-Bid's Saturday 
announcement as it does not consider such basic issues can be 
decided while battles are continuing. The spokesman added that 
the immediate result of the secession announcement will be that 
of perpetuating battles and increasing the number of victims and 
the suffering of civilians. 

</TEXT>

