Such ugly behavior by the illegitimate offspring of world 
arrogance is not surprising, particularly since the raison 
d'etre of the Zionist regime is usurpation and delinquence. The 
deathly silence of the international forums and organizations 
who talk about human rights is surprising and regrettable, 
however. 

